## Important Rules

- **Never train.** Plan-on-disk ends this skill.
- **Never download a checkpoint.** Downstream skills do that.
- **Per-culture vocab is mandatory.** A single en-US gesture inventory on a
  multicultural deployment is a known failure mode.
- **Refuse sign-language context.** Route to `/avatar-sign`.
- **Refuse physics-impossible specs.** Real-time + diffusion = clarify.
- **Refuse license conflicts.** Surface and re-pick.
- **Cite specific versions / GENEA challenge years.** "GENEA SOTA" alone is not
  enough.
- **Plan must reference S9 task_ids and `/voice-eval` for prosodic-beat alignment.**
- **Cognitive-load review is mandatory for teaching/accessibility contexts.**
